/// There are two files .env.dev and .env.prod in the root of this package
/// Create two new files and place your own keys. You may use different production and development keys

/// This file is an example on how the keys should look like
/// You need to have .env.dev and .env.prod with all the keys
/// Finally after placing all the keys you need to run the following command inside packages/env/ folder
/// $ dart run build_runner build
/// This will generate all the files. It may take a few minutes

SUPABASE_URL=YOUR_SUPABASE_URL
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
POWERSYNC_URL=YOUR_POWERSYNC_URL